────────────────────────────────────────────
Purpose
────────────────────────────────────────────

This form documents acknowledgement and acceptance of the AI Governance Guardrails for Healthcare Operations. It confirms that individuals using AI-assisted tools understand their responsibilities when supporting regulated healthcare workflows.


────────────────────────────────────────────
Scope
────────────────────────────────────────────

This acknowledgement applies to any individual using AI tools to support:
- Healthcare operations
- Revenue cycle activities
- Administrative or compliance workflows
- Documentation, drafting, or summarization tasks


────────────────────────────────────────────
Acknowledgement & Attestation
────────────────────────────────────────────

By signing below, I acknowledge and agree to the following:

[  ]  I will NOT enter, upload, or share PHI or PII with AI tools.  
      All inputs will be de-identified or generalized before use.

[  ]  I understand AI-generated content is draft support only.  
      AI does not replace professional judgment or source-system review.

[  ]  I am responsible for verification.  
      I will verify accuracy, completeness, and appropriateness before use or submission.

[  ]  I will escalate high-impact use cases.  
      This includes coverage decisions, billing, authorizations, denials, and patient communications.

[  ]  I will document AI usage.  
      I will log AI tool use according to the AI use log requirements.

[  ]  I understand accountability remains human.  
      Responsibility for decisions and outcomes remains with me, not the AI tool.


